{"tid":118221,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"「反手摸胸」測柔韌度　最後一位咁做令人O嘴","createTime":"2017-02-12T23:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T03:15:23.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"69e46a63460a20e505b21ff1146388f3ebe9bb72","tid":118221,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T23:45:29.000Z","msg":"有Youtuber四出測試少女的肢體柔韌度，分別要她們做「反手摸胸」及「自取其乳」兩個高難度動作，最後一位少女以騎呢方法完成考驗，令人睇到O晒嘴。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/02/20170209_PN_%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%AF%A6%E6%B8%AC05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F02%2F20170209_PN_%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E6%25B8%25AC05.jpg&h=5029def9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「反手摸胸」及「自取其乳」一直被網民視為神技，對人體柔韌度的要求極高，正確做法是這樣的：<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/02/20170209_PN_%E4%BB%A5%E6%89%8B%E8%87%AA%E6%91%B8%E5%85%B6%E8%83%B801.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F02%2F20170209_PN_%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2591%25B8%25E5%2585%25B6%25E8%2583%25B801.gif&h=c0ec16ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上圖片<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/02/20170209_PN_%E4%BB%A5%E6%89%8B%E8%87%AA%E6%91%B8%E5%85%B6%E8%83%B802.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F02%2F20170209_PN_%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2591%25B8%25E5%2585%25B6%25E8%2583%25B802.gif&h=4e631148&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這位Youtuber首先測試「反手摸胸」，結果很多少女都做不到。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/02/20170209_PN_%E4%BB%A5%E6%89%8B%E8%87%AA%E6%91%B8%E5%85%B6%E8%83%B803.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F02%2F20170209_PN_%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2591%25B8%25E5%2585%25B6%25E8%2583%25B803.gif&h=82c911d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/02/20170209_PN_%E4%BB%A5%E6%89%8B%E8%87%AA%E6%91%B8%E5%85%B6%E8%83%B804-1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F02%2F20170209_PN_%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2591%25B8%25E5%2585%25B6%25E8%2583%25B804-1.gif&h=2f479f48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/02/20170209_PN_%E4%BB%A5%E6%89%8B%E8%87%AA%E6%91%B8%E5%85%B6%E8%83%B805.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F02%2F20170209_PN_%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2591%25B8%25E5%2585%25B6%25E8%2583%25B805.gif&h=44a61851&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟著再考驗「自取其乳」的動作，接受測試的少女都做得頗為吃力，難道真是極少人可以做到這兩個動作嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/02/20170209_PN_%E4%BB%A5%E6%89%8B%E8%87%AA%E6%91%B8%E5%85%B6%E8%83%B808.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F02%2F20170209_PN_%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2591%25B8%25E5%2585%25B6%25E8%2583%25B808.gif&h=dfa30d80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/02/20170209_PN_%E4%BB%A5%E6%89%8B%E8%87%AA%E6%91%B8%E5%85%B6%E8%83%B807.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F02%2F20170209_PN_%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2591%25B8%25E5%2585%25B6%25E8%2583%25B807.gif&h=06831f2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/02/20170209_PN_%E4%BB%A5%E6%89%8B%E8%87%AA%E6%91%B8%E5%85%B6%E8%83%B806.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F02%2F20170209_PN_%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2591%25B8%25E5%2585%25B6%25E8%2583%25B806.gif&h=ca291fb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後，終於找到下面這一位可以用雙手做出「自取其乳」動作的人，不過，這位少女的做法並不標準，還相當騎呢取巧，讓網民們睇到O晒嘴。<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/02/20170209_PN_%E4%BB%A5%E6%89%8B%E8%87%AA%E6%91%B8%E5%85%B6%E8%83%B809.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F02%2F20170209_PN_%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2591%25B8%25E5%2585%25B6%25E8%2583%25B809.gif&h=13090d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n實測影片在上月中上載，在網友間熱傳，至今已吸引逾十七萬人瀏覽，有網友形容，最後一位是「韌性不夠，推胸來湊」，有網友則大讚她有創意，「動作零分，創意爆燈。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/9-plastic-post/1790214-%E3%80%8C%E5%8F%8D%E6%89%8B%E6%91%B8%E8%83%B8%E3%80%8D%E6%B8%AC%E6%9F%94%E9%9F%8C%E5%BA%A6-%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%8D%E5%92%81%E5%81%9A%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BAo%E5%98%B4?r=w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2F9-plastic-post%2F1790214-%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%2591%25B8%25E8%2583%25B8%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E6%259F%2594%25E9%259F%258C%25E5%25BA%25A6-%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BE%258C%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25BD%258D%25E5%2592%2581%25E5%2581%259A%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25BA%25BAo%25E5%2598%25B4%3Fr%3Dw&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=a32ce8c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/9-plastic-post/1790214-%E3%80%8C%E5%8F%8D%E6%89%8B%E6%91%B8%E8%83%B8%E3%80%8D%E6%B8%AC%E6%9F%94%E9%9F%8C%E5%BA%A6-%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%8D%E5%92%81%E5%81%9A%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BAo%E5%98%B4?r=w</a>"},{"pid":"40d35d6c96e59